{"tid":1345360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 宏揚國際：一鋪清算警隊惡行！","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:55:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T14:45:21.000Z","uid":281046,"like":72,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"f21b052fb98a1e59e1ebd5e87aec85522a1735d4","tid":1345360,"uid":281046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:55:02.000Z","msg":"以下歸納左幾點警隊六月至今嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">惡行</span>（可以加、減、改），求文宣<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">宏揚國際</span></span>:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 警察、黑社會、立法會議員聯手殘害市民</span>（港鐵角色？）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 商家容讓警察殘害市民</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 政府、警察聯手設局陷害市民</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4. 警察設局陷害市民</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">5. 香港警察持續違反人權、持政治立場、濫用警權、選擇性執法等</span> (自2014年起備受炮轟，但行為一直持續而沒有受到處分，甚至變本加厲)<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">a)警察行動違反人權</span> (國際特赦組織調查證明指控屬實 21/6)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">b) 警察假扮示威者，甚至帶頭/慫恿衝擊等示威行為 </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">c) 警員隨意截查人及對其搜身</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">d) 非法索取市民/病人資料（？）</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">e) 警員不依法執法</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">f ) 警員選擇性執法</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ng) 警員侮辱宗教<br />\neg. 牧師試圖隔開警民衝突 反遭警斥：叫你耶穌嚟見我 （12/6）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/340382/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%86%B6%E8%A9%A6%E5%9C%96%E9%9A%94%E9%96%8B%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%8F%8D%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%A5-%E5%8F%AB%E4%BD%A0%E8%80%B6%E7%A9%8C%E5%9A%9F%E8%A6%8B%E6%88%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F340382%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%2586%25B6%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E5%258F%25AB%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%2580%25B6%25E7%25A9%258C%25E5%259A%259F%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%2588%2591&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=9fa84a33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/340382/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%86%B6%E8%A9%A6%E5%9C%96%E9%9A%94%E9%96%8B%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%8F%8D%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%A5-%E5%8F%AB%E4%BD%A0%E8%80%B6%E7%A9%8C%E5%9A%9F%E8%A6%8B%E6%88%91</a>"},{"pid":"5960fe95008e92ce850548bed45e9c0795b6b46b","tid":1345360,"uid":284949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e4998dfe42ee1ba16d2ba7cc7a2f9d1aec5385","tid":1345360,"uid":284949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:57:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5f0f6e7276debeb494f7a6f2d59403135b1c8f","tid":1345360,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e89684e82059b92851aaf595b0cdd770b0e4eed","tid":1345360,"uid":281046,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:58:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">h) 警員不法對待被捕人士</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">i) 其他警員非法行為</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">6. a)警司協會、香港警務督協會、海外督察協會及警察隊員佐級協會強烈反對成立獨立調查委員會。（19/6）</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">b)投訴警察課</span>是「自己人查自己人」；由於在投訴課工作的警員一般會工作約3年，之後會被調走，日後或會遇上被投訴、職級高過自己的警員，所以<span style=\"color: blue;\">根本不敢處理投訴</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">c)監警會沒有正式調查權</span>，無法審視較高層的政治決定，亦不會調查示威者的行動。(2/7)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">d)監警會全面建制化</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">7. 議員/司長犯法不受調查</span>（呢點可能少少離題）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966e9bc908ad47d5bcfb5ea0122aa17226d5f931","tid":1345360,"uid":281046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d5f0f6e7276debeb494f7a6f2d594031