ash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash; 八大訴求 &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定義\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選\n六、要求永不落實「社會信用評分系統」\n七、要求移除全港「多功能智慧燈柱」\n八、追究元朗鄉黑暴徒及警察失蹤</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8d7744bf8d5c87cfda89726d52c4b3509933b43d","tid":1345360,"uid":281046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe91ce63c74f48d991d8101b3bf0cfe30f166fe0","tid":1345360,"uid":149630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"［無政府狀態］元朗恐怖襲擊將成民間自治催産士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1346084\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1346084</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86e1966ab9286cee739a357d162caacc0d88a455","tid":1345360,"uid":281046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb44df8ab9f08289bfa5c93fe71917c8d6533975","tid":1345360,"uid":237372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:49:06.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c898f1ac50a3968b83e56509d84ced188036ba4","tid":1345360,"uid":281046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e6905105bab834aaf84671d708e66995f42b494","tid":1345360,"uid":62889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:49:28.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed63e4425ccb1f166ce9e77c1f7e6492df31f19","tid":1345360,"uid":281046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"591b48948e0247eca9284821fb248d90bd0d8526","tid":1345360,"uid":136457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hk