an><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">c) 警員隨意截查人及對其搜身</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">d) 非法索取市民/病人資料（？）</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">e) 警員不依法執法</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">f ) 警員選擇性執法</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ng) 警員侮辱宗教<br />\neg. 牧師試圖隔開警民衝突 反遭警斥：叫你耶穌嚟見我 （12/6）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/340382/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%86%B6%E8%A9%A6%E5%9C%96%E9%9A%94%E9%96%8B%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%8F%8D%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%A5-%E5%8F%AB%E4%BD%A0%E8%80%B6%E7%A9%8C%E5%9A%9F%E8%A6%8B%E6%88%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F340382%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E7%2589%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E6%2586%25B6%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E5%259C%2596%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%2596%258B%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E5%258F%25AB%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E8%2580%25B6%25E7%25A9%258C%25E5%259A%259F%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%2588%2591&d=FZf2Eq7oNugCj0cVmX%2F%2FqdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=9fa84a33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/340382/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E7%89%A7%E5%B8%AB%E6%86%B6%E8%A9%A6%E5%9C%96%E9%9A%94%E9%96%8B%E8%AD%A6%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E5%8F%8D%E9%81%AD%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%A5-%E5%8F%AB%E4%BD%A0%E8%80%B6%E7%A9%8C%E5%9A%9F%E8%A6%8B%E6%88%91</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"我